'''苹果文件系统'''（{{lang-en|'''Ap'''ple '''F'''ile '''S'''ystem}}，简称'''APFS'''）是一个适用于[[OS_X|macOS]]、[[iOS|iOS]]、[[tvOS|tvOS]]和[[watchOS|watchOS]]的文件系统，目前正在由[[苹果公司|苹果公司]]开发和部署。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2017/3/27/15076244/apple-file-system-apfs-ios-10-3-features|title=Apple is upgrading millions of iOS devices to a new modern file system today|accessdate=2017-04-02|date=2017-03-27|work=The Verge|archive-date=2017-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170327184802/http://www.theverge.com/2017/3/27/15076244/apple-file-system-apfs-ios-10-3-features|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/16/06/13/apple-file-system-will-scale-from-apple-watch-to-macs-replace-hfs|title='Apple File System' will scale from Apple Watch to Macs, replace HFS+|author=Roger Fingas|date=June 13, 2016|publisher=[[Apple_Insider|Apple Insider]]|accessdate=2016-06-23|archive-date=2016-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160723030751/http://appleinsider.com/articles/16/06/13/apple-file-system-will-scale-from-apple-watch-to-macs-replace-hfs|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="digging-into-apfs">{{Cite web|url=http://arstechnica.co.uk/apple/2016/06/apfs-apple-new-file-system-dev-details/|title=Digging into APFS, Apple's new file system|date=13 June 2016|last=Hutchinson|first=Lee|website=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica UK]]|access-date=15 June 2016}}</ref>它的目的是解决[[HFS+|HFS+]]（Mac OS Extend，APFS的前身）文件系统的核心问题。<ref>{{cite web|title=进步与缺憾 资深开发者讲解苹果新文件系统|url=http://www.feng.com/iPhone/news/2016-06-27/Well-known-developers-take-you-analysis-apple-APFS-file-system-a-_650358.shtml|website=威锋网|accessdate=2016-06-29}}</ref>APFS针对[[闪存|闪存]]和[[固态硬盘|固态存储设备]]进行优化，具有[[寫入時複製|寫入時複製]]等设计特点，使用I/O合并改进性能。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://9to5mac.com/2016/06/13/apple-file-system-apfs/|title=Apple File System (APFS) announced for 2017, scales ‘from Apple Watch to Mac Pro’ and focuses on encryption|accessdate=2017-04-02|date=2016-06-13|last=Weintraub|first=Seth|work=9to5Mac|archive-date=2017-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170328195315/https://9to5mac.com/2016/06/13/apple-file-system-apfs/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://arstechnica.com/apple/2016/06/new-apfs-file-system-spotted-in-new-version-of-macos/|title=New file system spotted in macOS Sierra [Updated]|newspaper=Ars Technica|accessdate=2017-04-02|language=en-us|archive-date=2017-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170328195529/https://arstechnica.com/apple/2016/06/new-apfs-file-system-spotted-in-new-version-of-macos/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 特点 ==
苹果文件系统使用64位[[inode|inode]]号码，并允许使用更安全的存储。与HFS+类似，为了提供更好的空间管理与性能，APFS的代码使用[[TRIM命令|TRIM命令]]。由于APFS采用全新的数据计算方式，设备的读写速度与可用空间可能会因此提升。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.joe.co.uk/tech/updating-iphone-will-give-one-major-benefit-119704|title=Updating your iPhone will give you one major benefit|author=|date=|work=|newspaper=JOE.co.uk|accessdate=2017-06-09|language=en|archive-date=2017-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170520045551/https://www.joe.co.uk/tech/updating-iphone-will-give-one-major-benefit-119704|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 寫入時複製 ===
寫入時複製可以使文件系统快速、高效地在同个卷宗上复制文件，且不须占用额外存储空间。对数据的修改将写入其他位置，未修改的[[块_(数据存储)|块]]则继续共享使用。对文件的更改将使用[[差分編碼|差分編碼]]保存，减少文档修订和复制所需的存储空间。<ref name="digging-into-apfs">{{Cite web|url=http://arstechnica.co.uk/apple/2016/06/apfs-apple-new-file-system-dev-details/|title=Digging into APFS, Apple's new file system|date=13 June 2016|last=Hutchinson|first=Lee|website=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica UK]]|access-date=15 June 2016}}</ref>

=== 快照 ===
APFS支持创建特定时间点、文件系统只读实例的[[快照_(電腦儲存)|快照]]。<ref name="digging-into-apfs">{{Cite web|url=http://arstechnica.co.uk/apple/2016/06/apfs-apple-new-file-system-dev-details/|title=Digging into APFS, Apple's new file system|date=13 June 2016|last=Hutchinson|first=Lee|website=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica UK]]|access-date=15 June 2016}}</ref>

=== 加密 ===
APFS将实现文件和敏感[[元数据|元数据]]的[[磁盘加密|磁盘加密]]。它对一个容器中的每个卷支持下列[[加密|加密]]模型：
* 不加密
* [[单密钥|单密钥]]加密
* 多密钥加密，每个文件使用单独的密钥加密，[[元数据|元数据]]再使用另一个密钥加密。<ref name="digging-into-apfs">{{Cite web|url=http://arstechnica.co.uk/apple/2016/06/apfs-apple-new-file-system-dev-details/|title=Digging into APFS, Apple's new file system|date=13 June 2016|last=Hutchinson|first=Lee|website=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica UK]]|access-date=15 June 2016}}</ref>

=== 数据完整性 ===
APFS利用现代硬件固件中强大的[[校验和|校验和]]和[[错误纠正|错误纠正]]的优势。为确保[[完整性|数据完整性]]，APFS 对元数据采用校验和技术，但未同时对用户数据采用。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://dtrace.org/blogs/ahl/2016/06/19/apfs-part5/|title=APFS in Detail: Data Integrity|author=Adam Leventhal|date=June 19, 2016|accessdate=2016-06-23|archive-date=2016-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160621060302/http://dtrace.org/blogs/ahl/2016/06/19/apfs-part5/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== -{zh-hant:當機;zh-hans:崩溃}-防护 ===
APFS被设计为可以免受-{zh-hant:當機;zh-hans:崩溃}-带来的数据损失。它使用“写入全新的元数据记录、指向新的记录、释放旧的记录”的逻辑，而非直接覆盖现有的记录。这能避免更新期间-{zh-hant:當機;zh-hans:崩溃}-而导致的记录损坏，也能防止重复写入两次更改（HFS+日志文件系统需要将更改先写入日志，再写入目录文件）。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://dtrace.org/blogs/ahl/2016/06/19/apfs-part5/|title=APFS in Detail: Data Integrity|accessdate=2017-06-09|author=|date=|work=dtrace.org|publisher=|archive-date=2016-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160621060302/http://dtrace.org/blogs/ahl/2016/06/19/apfs-part5/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 限制与不足 ==
第一代APFS不为用户数据提供[[校验和|校验和]]，但通过基于[[元数据|元数据]]的校验和检查来确保数据完整。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://arstechnica.com/apple/2016/06/a-zfs-developers-analysis-of-the-good-and-bad-in-apples-new-apfs-file-system/|title=A ZFS developer’s analysis of the good and bad in Apple’s new APFS file system|newspaper=Ars Technica|accessdate=2017-01-28|language=en-us}}</ref>另外，它并不利用[[易失性存储器|易失性存储器]]可比特寻址这一特性，也不支持[[数据压缩|压缩]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.zdnet.com/article/why-apples-apfs-wont-last-30-years/|title=Why Apple's APFS won't last 30 years {{!}} ZDNet|accessdate=2017-01-28|last=Harris|first=Robin|work=ZDNet|language=en|archive-date=2017-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170406190806/http://www.zdnet.com/article/why-apples-apfs-wont-last-30-years/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

与HFS+不同的是，在[[macOS_High_Sierra|macOS High Sierra]]测试版本之前，APFS不进行[[Unicode等價性#.E6.AD.A3.E8.A6.8F.E5.8C.96|Unicode正规化]]，<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://mjtsai.com/blog/2017/03/24/apfss-bag-of-bytes-filenames/|title=APFS's "Bag of Bytes' Filenames|accessdate=2017-06-09|author=|date=|last=Tsai|first=Michael J.|work=mjtsai.com|publisher=|language=en}}</ref>无法支持大多数非英语语言。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://eclecticlight.co/2017/04/06/apfs-is-currently-unusable-with-most-non-english-languages/|title=APFS is currently unusable with most non-English languages|accessdate=2017-06-09|date=2017-04-06|last=hoakley|work=The Eclectic Light Company|archive-date=2017-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170608180050/https://eclecticlight.co/2017/04/06/apfs-is-currently-unusable-with-most-non-english-languages/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2017/715/|title=What's new in Apple File System - WWDC 2017 - Videos - Apple Developer|accessdate=2017-08-03|last=Inc.|first=Apple|work=Apple Developer|language=en-US}}</ref>

== 操作系统支持 ==

=== macOS ===
APFS于[[macOS_Sierra|macOS Sierra]]中提供，但存在一些限制：

* 使用macOS Sierra格式化所得到的磁盘可能并不会与未来版本的macOS兼容，并也可能不与macOS的最终版本兼容。
* APFS的可用选项有“区分大小写”，“加密”，“区分大小写，加密”。
* 关于[[時光機_(macOS)|Time Machine]]：[[macOS_Catalina|macOS Catalina]] (10.15) 及先前版本不能备份到 APFS 格式的磁盘<ref>{{Cite web|title=在 Mac 上可以与时间机器配合使用的磁盘类型|url=https://support.apple.com/zh-cn/guide/mac-help/mh15139/10.15/mac/10.15|accessdate=2020-07-15|work=Apple Support|language=zh-CN}}</ref>，而在[[macOS_Big_Sur|macOS Big Sur]]（11）中支持备份至APFS格式的硬盘<ref>{{Cite web|title=APFS changes affect Time Machine in macOS Big Sur, encrypted drives in iOS 14|url=https://appleinsider.com/articles/20/06/27/apfs-changes-affect-time-machine-in-macos-big-sur-encrypted-drives-in-ios-14|accessdate=2020-07-15|work=AppleInsider|language=en}}</ref>。
* macOS 10.14 前的系統不兼容[[Fusion_Drive|Fusion Drive]]。
* 在macOS的磁盘工具中，可通过“菜单-编辑-转换为APFS”无损把HFS+分区转换为APFS分区，但不能无损把APFS分区转换回HFS+分区。
在macOS Sierra中可使用<code>diskutil</code>命令行工具将分区格式化为APFS。APFS 在 [[macOS_High_Sierra|macOS High Sierra]]（10.13）之後將成為預設的檔案格式。

=== iOS、tvOS与watchOS ===
所有兼容的设备升级到[[IOS_10|iOS 10.3]]、[[TvOS|tvOS 10.2]]和[[WatchOS|watchOS 3.2]]，会将HFS+文件系统转换为APFS。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.macrumors.com/2017/03/27/apple-releases-ios-10-3/|title=Apple Releases iOS 10.3 With Find My AirPods, APFS, App Store Review Tweaks and More|accessdate=2017-04-02|last=Clover|first=Juli|archive-date=2017-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170327194444/https://www.macrumors.com/2017/03/27/apple-releases-ios-10-3/|dead-url=no}}</ref>有测试表明APFS不支持32位的设备，例如iPhone 5<ref>{{Citation|last=Andrle|first=Tomas|title=TestIOSAPFSCheck: Trying to programmatically detect if filesystem is APFS|date=2017-06-02|url=https://github.com/catnapgames/TestIOSAPFSCheck|accessdate=2017-06-09}}{{Dead link|date=2018年9月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

